{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1587,"text":"Two hundred years of modern science."},{"time":5678,"text":"We have to admit"},{"time":6853,"text":"that our performance is not great."},{"time":8995,"text":"The machines we build continue\nto suffer from mechanical failures."},{"time":13109,"text":"The houses we build\ndo not survive severe earthquakes."},{"time":17322,"text":"But we shouldn't be so critical\nof our scientists for a simple reason:"},{"time":21817,"text":"they didn't have much time."},{"time":24080,"text":"Two hundred years is not a lot of time,"},{"time":26424,"text":"while nature had three billion years"},{"time":29671,"text":"to perfect some of the most\namazing materials,"},{"time":33297,"text":"that we wish we had in our possession."},{"time":36262,"text":"Remember, these materials\ncarry a quality assurance"},{"time":40926,"text":"of three billion years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":43694,"text":"Take, for example, sequoia trees."},{"time":45549,"text":"They carry hundreds of tons\nfor hundreds of years"},{"time":50243,"text":"in cold weather, in warm climates,"},{"time":53185,"text":"UV light."},{"time":54552,"text":"Yet, if you look at the structure\nby high-resolution electron microscopy,"},{"time":59149,"text":"and you ask yourself, what is it made of,"},{"time":62196,"text":"surprisingly, it's made of sugar."},{"time":64992,"text":"Well, not exactly as we drink in our tea."},{"time":67825,"text":"It's actually a nanofiber\ncalled nanocrystalline cellulose."},{"time":71760,"text":"And this nanocrystalline cellulose\nis so strong, on a weight basis,"},{"time":77749,"text":"it's about 10 times stronger than steel."},{"time":81092,"text":"Yet it's made of sugar."}]},{"cues":[{"time":83541,"text":"So scientists all over the world\nbelieve that nanocellulose"},{"time":87386,"text":"is going to be one of the most important\nmaterials for the entire industry."},{"time":92328,"text":"But here's the problem:"},{"time":93796,"text":"say you want to buy\na half a ton of nanocellulose"},{"time":96821,"text":"to build a boat or an airplane."},{"time":98852,"text":"Well, you can Google, you can eBay,\nyou can even Alibaba."},{"time":103551,"text":"You won't find it."},{"time":105189,"text":"Of course, you're going to find\nthousands of scientific papers --"},{"time":108819,"text":"great papers, where scientists\nare going to say this is a great material,"},{"time":113660,"text":"there are lots of things\nwe can do with it."},{"time":115788,"text":"But no commercial source."}]},{"cues":[{"time":118286,"text":"So we at the Hebrew University,\ntogether with our partners in Sweden,"},{"time":122998,"text":"decided to focus on the development\nof an industrial-scale process"},{"time":128673,"text":"to produce this nanocellulose."},{"time":131093,"text":"And, of course,\nwe didn't want to cut trees."},{"time":134251,"text":"So we were looking for another source"},{"time":136974,"text":"of raw material,"},{"time":138350,"text":"and we found one -- in fact,\nthe sludge of the paper industry."},{"time":143617,"text":"The reason: there is a lot of it."},{"time":146159,"text":"Europe alone produces 11 million tons"},{"time":149993,"text":"of that material annually."},{"time":152447,"text":"It's the equivalent of a mountain\nthree kilometers high,"},{"time":157078,"text":"sitting on a soccer field."},{"time":159039,"text":"And we produce this mountain every year."},{"time":161693,"text":"So for everybody,\nit's an environmental problem,"},{"time":165194,"text":"and for us, it's a gold mine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":168923,"text":"So now, we are actually producing,\non an industrial scale in Israel,"},{"time":173109,"text":"nanocellulose, and very soon, in Sweden."},{"time":175684,"text":"We can do a lot of things\nwith the material."},{"time":177858,"text":"For example,"},{"time":179257,"text":"we have shown that by adding\nonly a small percent of nanocellulose"},{"time":183677,"text":"into cotton fibers, the same\nas my shirt is made of,"},{"time":187595,"text":"it increases its strength dramatically."},{"time":190611,"text":"So this can be used\nfor making amazing things,"},{"time":195834,"text":"like super-fabrics for industrial\nand medical applications."},{"time":201019,"text":"But this is not the only thing."},{"time":202937,"text":"For example, self-standing,\nself-supporting structures,"},{"time":206815,"text":"like the shelters that you can see now,"},{"time":209435,"text":"actually are now showcasing\nin the Venice Biennale for Architecture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":216702,"text":"Nature actually didn't stop its wonders"},{"time":220683,"text":"in the plant kingdom."},{"time":223144,"text":"Think about insects."},{"time":224515,"text":"Cat fleas, for example,"},{"time":226110,"text":"have the ability to jump\nabout a hundred times their height."},{"time":230863,"text":"That's amazing."},{"time":232343,"text":"It's the equivalent of a person"},{"time":234963,"text":"standing in the middle\nof Liberty Island in New York,"},{"time":239033,"text":"and in a single jump,"},{"time":240612,"text":"going to the top of the Statue of Liberty."},{"time":244776,"text":"I'm sure everybody would like to do that."},{"time":247236,"text":"So the question is:"},{"time":248559,"text":"How do cat fleas do it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":250941,"text":"It turns out, they make\nthis wonderful material,"},{"time":254235,"text":"which is called resilin."},{"time":256467,"text":"In simple words, resilin,\nwhich is a protein,"},{"time":260104,"text":"is the most elastic rubber on Earth."},{"time":265565,"text":"You can stretch it,"},{"time":267757,"text":"you can squish it,"},{"time":269408,"text":"and it doesn't lose almost any energy\nto the environment."},{"time":273699,"text":"When you release it -- snap!"},{"time":275556,"text":"It brings back all the energy."},{"time":278201,"text":"So I'm sure everybody\nwould like to have that material."},{"time":281116,"text":"But here's the problem:"},{"time":283529,"text":"to catch cat fleas is difficult."}]},{"cues":[{"time":285442,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":287408,"text":"Why? Because they are jumpy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":289269,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":291466,"text":"But now, it's actually\nenough to catch one."},{"time":296653,"text":"Now we can extract its DNA"},{"time":298773,"text":"and read how cat fleas make the resilin,"},{"time":301905,"text":"and clone it into a less-jumpy\norganism like a plant."},{"time":307669,"text":"So that's exactly what we did."},{"time":309378,"text":"Now we have the ability\nto produce lots of resilin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":313348,"text":"Well, my team decided to do something\nreally cool at the university."},{"time":317749,"text":"They decided to combine"},{"time":319102,"text":"the strongest material\nproduced by the plant kingdom"},{"time":322348,"text":"with the most elastic material\nproduced by the insect kingdom --"},{"time":326902,"text":"nanocellulose with resilin."},{"time":329420,"text":"And the result is amazing."},{"time":331691,"text":"This material, in fact, is tough,\nelastic and transparent."},{"time":338181,"text":"So there are lots of things\nthat can be done with this material."},{"time":341446,"text":"For example, next-generation sport shoes,"},{"time":343620,"text":"so we can jump higher, run faster."},{"time":346800,"text":"And even touch screens\nfor computers and smartphones,"},{"time":351409,"text":"that won't break."}]},{"cues":[{"time":352807,"text":"Well, the problem is,\nwe continue to implant"},{"time":356815,"text":"synthetic implants in our body,"},{"time":358927,"text":"which we glue and screw into our body."},{"time":362514,"text":"And I'm going to say\nthat this is not a good idea."},{"time":364885,"text":"Why? Because they fail."},{"time":367103,"text":"This synthetic material fails,"},{"time":368583,"text":"just like this plastic fork,"},{"time":371465,"text":"that is not strong enough\nfor its performance."},{"time":374483,"text":"But sometimes they are too strong,"},{"time":376173,"text":"and therefore their mechanical\nproperties do not really fit"},{"time":379268,"text":"their surrounding tissues."}]},{"cues":[{"time":381671,"text":"But in fact, the reason\nis much more fundamental."},{"time":384810,"text":"The reason is that in nature,"},{"time":387533,"text":"there is no one there"},{"time":389436,"text":"that actually takes my head\nand screws it onto my neck,"},{"time":393727,"text":"or takes my skin\nand glues it onto my body."},{"time":397413,"text":"In nature, everything is self-assembled."},{"time":400600,"text":"So every living cell,"},{"time":402494,"text":"whether coming from a plant,\ninsect or human being,"},{"time":407152,"text":"has a DNA that encodes\nfor nanobio building blocks."},{"time":411259,"text":"Many times they are proteins."},{"time":413318,"text":"Other times, they are enzymes\nthat make other materials,"},{"time":416973,"text":"like polysaccharides, fatty acids."},{"time":419783,"text":"And the common feature\nabout all these materials"},{"time":423189,"text":"is that they need no one."},{"time":425660,"text":"They recognize each other\nand self-assemble"},{"time":428630,"text":"into structures -- scaffolds\non which cells are proliferating"},{"time":433553,"text":"to give tissues."},{"time":435017,"text":"They develop into organs,\nand together bring life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":440115,"text":"So we at the Hebrew University,\nabout 10 years ago, decided to focus"},{"time":445080,"text":"on probably the most important\nbiomaterial for humans,"},{"time":450998,"text":"which is collagen."},{"time":453142,"text":"Why collagen?"},{"time":454356,"text":"Because collagen accounts for\nabout 25 percent of our dry weight."},{"time":458094,"text":"We have nothing more than collagen,\nother than water, in our body."},{"time":462611,"text":"So I always like to say,"},{"time":464608,"text":"anyone who is in the replacement\nparts of human beings"},{"time":467727,"text":"would like to have collagen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":469749,"text":"Admittedly, before we started our project,"},{"time":472711,"text":"there were already more\nthan 1,000 medical implants"},{"time":476378,"text":"made of collagen."},{"time":477804,"text":"You know, simple things like\ndermal fillers to reduce wrinkles,"},{"time":481684,"text":"augment lips,"},{"time":483087,"text":"and other, more sophisticated\nmedical implants, like heart valves."},{"time":487906,"text":"So where is the problem?"},{"time":490076,"text":"Well, the problem is the source."},{"time":492330,"text":"The source of all that collagen"},{"time":494679,"text":"is actually coming from dead bodies:"},{"time":497645,"text":"dead pigs, dead cows"},{"time":500548,"text":"and even human cadavers."},{"time":502342,"text":"So safety is a big issue."},{"time":505701,"text":"But it's not the only one."},{"time":507709,"text":"Also, the quality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":509756,"text":"Now here, I have a personal interest."},{"time":512415,"text":"This is my father, Zvi,\nin our winery in Israel."},{"time":515792,"text":"A heart valve, very similar\nto the one that I showed you before,"},{"time":519668,"text":"seven years ago,\nwas implanted in his body."},{"time":523941,"text":"Now, the scientific literature says\nthat these heart valves start to fail"},{"time":529101,"text":"10 years after the operation."},{"time":532446,"text":"No wonder:"},{"time":534295,"text":"they are made from old, used tissues,"},{"time":538426,"text":"just like this wall made of bricks\nthat is falling apart."},{"time":542778,"text":"Yeah, of course, I can take\nthose bricks and build a new wall."},{"time":546749,"text":"But it's not going to be the same."},{"time":548670,"text":"So the US Food and Drug Administration"},{"time":553140,"text":"made a notice already in 2007,"},{"time":555838,"text":"asking the companies to start to look\nfor better alternatives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":560291,"text":"So that's exactly what we did."},{"time":562892,"text":"We decided to clone all the five\nhuman genes responsible"},{"time":567558,"text":"for making type I collagen in humans"},{"time":571506,"text":"into a transgenic tobacco plant."},{"time":575462,"text":"So now, the plant has the ability\nto make human collagen brand new,"},{"time":581248,"text":"untouched."},{"time":582428,"text":"This is amazing."},{"time":584409,"text":"Actually, it's happening now."},{"time":586899,"text":"Today in Israel, we grow it\nin 25,000 square meters of greenhouses"},{"time":592039,"text":"all over the country."},{"time":593689,"text":"The farmers receive\nsmall plantlets of tobacco."},{"time":596541,"text":"It looks exactly like regular tobacco,"},{"time":598896,"text":"except that they have five human genes."},{"time":601459,"text":"They're responsible for making\ntype I collagen."},{"time":604691,"text":"We grow them for about 50 to 70 days,"},{"time":608628,"text":"we harvest the leaves,"},{"time":610540,"text":"and then the leaves are transported\nby cooling trucks to the factory."},{"time":614809,"text":"There, the process of extracting\nthe collagen starts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":618555,"text":"Now, if you ever made a pesto --\nessentially, the same thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":622066,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":624198,"text":"You crush the leaves, you get\nthe juice that contains the collagen."},{"time":628411,"text":"We concentrate the protein,"},{"time":630329,"text":"transfer the protein to clean rooms\nfor the final purification,"},{"time":633620,"text":"and the end result is a collagen\nidentical to what we have in our body --"},{"time":639956,"text":"untouched, brand new"},{"time":642201,"text":"and from which we make\ndifferent medical implants:"},{"time":645656,"text":"bone void fillers, for example,"},{"time":648135,"text":"for severe bone fractures, spinal fusion."},{"time":653068,"text":"And more recently, even,"},{"time":654657,"text":"we've been able to launch\ninto the market here in Europe"},{"time":659790,"text":"a flowable gel that is used\nfor diabetic foot ulcers,"},{"time":663651,"text":"that is now approved\nfor use in the clinic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":666823,"text":"This is not science fiction."},{"time":668716,"text":"This is happening now."},{"time":670391,"text":"We are using plants\nto make medical implants"},{"time":674961,"text":"for replacement parts for human beings."},{"time":677660,"text":"In fact, more recently,\nwe've been able to make collagen fibers"},{"time":682095,"text":"which are six times stronger\nthan the Achilles tendon."},{"time":685796,"text":"That's amazing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":687141,"text":"Together with our partners from Ireland,"},{"time":690047,"text":"we thought about the next thing:"},{"time":692112,"text":"adding resilin to those fibers."},{"time":695311,"text":"By doing that,"},{"time":696632,"text":"we've been able to make a superfiber"},{"time":699454,"text":"which is about 380 percent tougher,"},{"time":702775,"text":"and 300 percent more elastic."},{"time":706133,"text":"So oddly enough, in the future,"},{"time":708615,"text":"when a patient is transplanted\nwith artificial tendons or ligaments"},{"time":713599,"text":"made from these fibers,"},{"time":715809,"text":"we'll have better performance\nafter the surgery"},{"time":718956,"text":"than we had before the injury."}]},{"cues":[{"time":721642,"text":"So what's for the future?"},{"time":723391,"text":"In the future, we believe\nwe'll be able to make"},{"time":726416,"text":"many nanobio building blocks\nthat nature provided for us --"},{"time":730017,"text":"collagen, nanocellulose,\nresilin and many more."},{"time":734230,"text":"And that will enable us to make\nbetter machines perform better,"},{"time":738097,"text":"even the heart."},{"time":739651,"text":"Now, this heart\nis not going to be the same"},{"time":742121,"text":"as we can get from a donor."},{"time":744977,"text":"It will be better."},{"time":746834,"text":"It actually will perform better"},{"time":748890,"text":"and will last longer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":750945,"text":"My friend Zion Suliman once told me"},{"time":753414,"text":"a smart sentence."},{"time":756301,"text":"He said, \"If you want a new idea,"},{"time":759362,"text":"you should open an old book.\""},{"time":761431,"text":"And I'm going to say\nthat the book was written."},{"time":765815,"text":"It was written over three billion years"},{"time":767980,"text":"of evolution."},{"time":769566,"text":"And the text is the DNA of life."},{"time":773923,"text":"All we have to do"},{"time":775816,"text":"is read this text,"},{"time":778156,"text":"embrace nature's gift to us"},{"time":780737,"text":"and start our progress from here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":783252,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":784437,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}